          | office flower.
          | You absolutely need to water it every
          span(property='days') 2
          | days
          br
          span Current Plant humidity 67%. 
          img.small(src="img/flower_happy.png", height="20px")   
          p#flowerPosition
      
      hr

      div#stockIndicator.thing.row(typeof='Product')
        div.col-xs-6
          img(src='img/lamp.png' alt="Stock Indicator")
        div.description.col-xs-6
          h2(property='name') Stock Indicator
          |         
          br
          | Currently looking at the 
          strong(property='stockname') VW 
          | stock : 
          div#lampControls
            div(data-toggle="buttons").btn-group.button-color
                label.btn.btn-success(href='#', onclick="on('stockIndicator')") BUY
                    input(name="color",itemue="btn btn-default",type="radio")
                label.btn.btn-warning(href='#', onclick="off('stockIndicator')") SELL
